    "## 12. Calibration scatter plots\n",
    "\n",
    "Reference vs. calibrated PM₂.₅ for the validation and test sets. The dashed line is the 1:1 reference; points on it are perfect calibrations. R², MAE and RMSE are shown in the corner. Plots are displayed only (nothing is saved).\n"
   ]
